<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFS._Corkin1968">S. Corkin (1968). "Acquisition of motor skill after bilateral medial temporal-lobe excision". <i>Neuropsychologia</i> <b>6</b> (6): 255–265. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2F0028-3932%2868%2990024-9" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2F0028-3932%2868%2990024-9" rel="nofollow">10.1016/0028-3932(68)90024-9</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Acquisition+of+motor+skill+after+bilateral+medial+temporal-lobe+excision&amp;rft.jtitle=Neuropsychologia&amp;rft.aulast=S.+Corkin&amp;rft.au=S.+Corkin&amp;rft.date=1968&amp;rft.volume=6&amp;rft.issue=6&amp;rft.pages=255%26ndash%3B265&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1016%2F0028-3932%2868%2990024-9&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:HM_(patient)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
